# Supply chain workspace split

`Workspace.vue` is being split incrementally under `resources/js/pages/inventory-procurement/workspace/`.

## Pattern

1. **Tab UI** → `Workspace{Tab}Tab.vue` (lazy via `workspaceTabComponents.ts`)
2. **Shared state** → register on `bindInventoryWorkspace()` in parent; tabs read via `useInventoryWorkspace()`
3. **Tab-only helpers** → `workspaceOverview.ts`, `useRequestPipelineCounts.ts`, etc.
4. **Select helpers** → `workspace/constants.ts` (`EMPTY_SELECT_VALUE`, `toSelectValue`, `fromSelectValue`)

## Adding a new tab extract

- Copy tab markup from `Workspace.vue` into `Workspace{Name}Tab.vue`
- Prefix bindings with `ws.` from `useInventoryWorkspace()`
- Add required keys to `bindInventoryWorkspace({ ... })` in `Workspace.vue`
- Register async component in `workspaceTabComponents.ts`
- Replace inline `TabsContent` with `<Workspace{Name}Tab v-if="activeTab === '{tab}'" />`

## Extracted tabs (lazy-loaded)

All primary workspace tabs: `overview`, `requisitions`, `shortage-queue`, `transfers`, `inventory`, `ledger`, `department-stock`, `procurement`, `msd-orders`, `lead-times`, `claims`, `analytics`

## Extracted overlays

`WorkspaceFilterOverlays.vue` — inventory filters sheet, mobile procurement drawer, mobile ledger drawer

## Extracted auxiliary sheets

`WorkspaceAuxiliarySheets.vue` — create batch, record lead time, record delivery, barcode scanner

## Extracted transfer sheets

`WorkspaceTransferSheets.vue` — create transfer, update transfer status, variance review

## Extracted request entry sheets

`WorkspaceRequestEntrySheets.vue` — create department requisition, create procurement request

## Extracted inventory ops sheets

`WorkspaceInventoryOpsSheets.vue` — create inventory item, record stock movement, reconcile stock count

## Extracted requisition details sheet

`WorkspaceRequisitionDetailsSheet.vue` — department requisition review, approve/reject/issue workflow

## Extracted procurement lifecycle sheets

`WorkspaceProcurementLifecycleSheets.vue` — place order, receive goods, update status, request details (with audit log panel)

## Extracted item details sheet

`WorkspaceItemDetailsSheet.vue` — item overview, edit, status, batches, audit trail sub-tabs

## Extracted claims and MSD sheets

`WorkspaceClaimsAndMsdSheets.vue` — dispensing claim link, MSD electronic order

## Still inline

None — all workspace sheets/overlays extracted; parent holds network logic via `bindInventoryWorkspace()`

## Do not

- Move dialogs/sheets out until tab lists are stable
- Duplicate `apiRequest` — keep network logic in parent until a composable extract is planned
